      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIMMY TESLA (2) turned in a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Brave Annie (23.01) in a OPEN. Placed at his previous run. Has ability and looks hard to stop. TRUST ME (8) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 27.58 beating Myles Keeping. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. LINGUINE MONELLI (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (30.36) in a Free For All at Cannington. Solid record at the distance winning 12 races. Has won four of eight starts from this draw. Can figure in the finish. PURSUIT SPECIAL (4) cannot be ruled out.",
